{"id":128,"date":"2020-01-11T18:13:06","date_gmt":"2020-01-11T11:13:06","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/thocaca.com\/?p=128"},"modified":"2021-08-22T08:21:44","modified_gmt":"2021-08-22T01:21:44","slug":"tai-lieu-mon-ngu-van-thap-cam","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2020\/01\/11\/tai-lieu-mon-ngu-van-thap-cam\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u m\u00f4n Ng\u1eef V\u0103n th\u1eadp c\u1ea9m!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Do m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u, m\u00e0 c\u1ee9 \u0111\u0103ng l\u1ebb l\u1ebb th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o m\u1edbi h\u1ebft. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1eebng c\u00e1i th\u00ec m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 nh\u1ecf gi\u1ecdt. Th\u00f4i th\u00ec m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng c\u1ea3 file t\u1ed5ng lu\u00f4n cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tha h\u1ed3 ch\u1ecdn. Th\u00edch g\u00ec th\u00ec v\u00e0o ch\u1ecdn nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u00ec m\u00f4n Ng\u1eef V\u0103n nhi\u1ec1u khi ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m theo c\u1ea3m t\u00ednh, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e0i v\u0103n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ee7 \u00fd, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea1ch v\u0103n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea5m th\u00ec c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111i\u1ec3m cao l\u1eafm. Cho n\u00ean m\u00ecnh ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecdc nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ecdc v\u0103n m\u1eabu \u1ea5y \u1ea1. Xem nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ea1ch v\u0103n, c\u00e1ch vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng vi\u1ebft \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ecdc nhi\u1ec1u th\u00ec c\u00e1ch vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9 ch\u0103m ch\u0103m v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3. Th\u00e0nh ra c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0103n thua l\u1eafm \u0111\u00e2u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd n\u00f3i c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n khi l\u00e0m b\u00e0i th\u00ec copy m\u1ed7i ch\u1ed7 m\u1ed7i t\u00ed \u0111\u00e2u nh\u00e9. M\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ecdc nhi\u1ec1u cho m\u1ea1ch v\u0103n th\u00eam phong ph\u00fa th\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea5y. Ch\u1ee9 copy v\u00e0o r\u1ed3i th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i nham nh\u1edf ra th\u00ec ch\u1ebft d\u1edf \ud83d\ude09<br><a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/open?id=0BwnPNU3NInlpRDc4QzdWZ0lXYnM\">https:\/\/drive.google.com\/open?id=0BwnPNU3NInlpRDc4QzdWZ0lXYnM<\/a><br>Ch\u00fac m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on the_content --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on the_content -->","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>Do m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u, m\u00e0 c\u1ee9 \u0111\u0103ng l\u1ebb l\u1ebb th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o m\u1edbi h\u1ebft. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1eebng c\u00e1i <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2020\/01\/11\/tai-lieu-mon-ngu-van-thap-cam\/\" title=\"T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u m\u00f4n Ng\u1eef V\u0103n th\u1eadp c\u1ea9m!\">[&#8230;]<\/a><!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":132,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[13,4],"tags":[43,21],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/128"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=128"}],"version-history":[{"count":1